Dialogue: 0.0:00:04.33.0:00:09.15.Main.Ijichi.0000.0000.0000..Our window verified the \Ncurse womb three hours ago.
Dialogue: 0.0:00:09.92.0:00:12.39.Main.Ijichi.0000.0000.0000..Once 90 percent were successfully evacuated.
Dialogue: 0.0:00:12.39.0:00:15.14.Main.Ijichi.0000.0000.0000..they made the call to seal off the center.
Dialogue: 0.0:00:15.61.0:00:18.03.Main.Car.0000.0000.0000..{\an8\c&H260D8E&}Road Closed
Dialogue: 0.0:00:15.95.0:00:19.89.Main.Ijichi.0000.0000.0000..Citizens within a 500-meter radius \Nhave been evacuated. as well.
Dialogue: 0.0:00:21.31.0:00:22.81.Main.Yuuji.0000.0000.0000..Ijichi-san. question.
Dialogue: 0.0:00:23.13.0:00:24.68.Main.Yuuji.0000.0000.0000..What's a "window" here?
Dialogue: 0.0:00:24.93.0:00:29.72.Main.Ijichi.0000.0000.0000..A window is a member of \NJujutsu Tech who can see curses.
Dialogue: 0.0:00:30.06.0:00:31.74.Main.Ijichi.0000.0000.0000..They aren't sorcerers. though.
Dialogue: 0.0:00:31.94.0:00:33.62.Main.Yuuji.0000.0000.0000..Oh. okay.
Dialogue: 0.0:00:33.62.0:00:34.84.Main.Ijichi.0000.0000.0000..Let's continue.
Dialogue: 0.0:00:35.69.0:00:37.70.Main.Ijichi.0000.0000.0000..Detainee Block 2.
Dialogue: 0.0:00:38.34.0:00:43.31.Main.Ijichi.0000.0000.0000..At present. five detainees \Nremain there with the curse womb.
Dialogue: 0.0:00:43.67.0:00:46.30.Main.Ijichi.0000.0000.0000..If this curse womb is the \Ntype that metamorphoses.
Dialogue: 0.0:00:46.71.0:00:50.48.Main.Ijichi.0000.0000.0000..we predict it will become \Na special-grade cursed spirit.
Dialogue: 0.0:00:50.90.0:00:51.99.Italics.Both.0000.0000.0000..Special-grade...
Dialogue: 0.0:00:52.45.0:00:56.90.Main.Yuuji.0000.0000.0000..Hey. so... I still don't really understand \Nwhat "special-grade" means.
Dialogue: 0.0:00:58.00.0:01:01.42.Main.Ijichi.0000.0000.0000..Then allow me to explain it so \Neven idiots can understand.
Dialogue: 0.0:00:58.70.0:01:08.46.sign_1408_21__If_Conventional.ScreenTop.0000.0000.0000..{\fscx90}*If Conventional Weapons Were Effective Against Cursed Spirits
Dialogue: 0.0:00:58.70.0:01:08.46.sign_1408_22_Grade_4.Screencenter.0000.0000.0000..{\fad(1.226)\pos(114.173)}Grade 4
Dialogue: 0.0:00:58.70.0:01:08.46.sign_1408_23_A_Wooden_Bat_is_.Screencenter.0000.0000.0000..{\fad(1.226)\pos(112.193)}A wooden bat is enough
Dialogue: 0.0:00:58.70.0:01:08.46.sign_1408_22_Grade_4.Screenbottom.0000.0000.0000..{\fad(1.226)\pos(114.274)\3c&HCAE25D&}Grade 3
Dialogue: 0.0:00:58.70.0:01:08.46.sign_1408_23_A_Wooden_Bat_is_.Screenbottom.0000.0000.0000..{\fad(1.226)\pos(112.294)\q2}If you have a handgun. you can rest easy
Dialogue: 0.0:01:02.08.0:01:03.49.Main.Ijichi.0000.0000.0000..First. there's grade 4.
Dialogue: 0.0:01:03.49.0:01:05.39.Main.Ijichi.0000.0000.0000..A wooden bat is enough for them.
Dialogue: 0.0:01:05.39.0:01:06.29.Main.Ijichi.0000.0000.0000..Grade 3.
Dialogue: 0.0:01:06.29.0:01:08.18.Main.Ijichi.0000.0000.0000..If you have a handgun. you can rest easy.
Dialogue: 0.0:01:08.29.0:01:13.96.sign_1408_22_Grade_4.Screentop.0000.0000.0000..{\fad(695.226)\3c&HCAE25D&\pos(112.48.667)}Grade 3
Dialogue: 0.0:01:08.29.0:01:13.96.sign_1408_23_A_Wooden_Bat_is_.Screentop.0000.0000.0000..{\fad(695.226)\q2\pos(114.70)}If you have a handgun. you can rest easy
Dialogue: 0.0:01:08.29.0:01:13.96.sign_1408_22_Grade_4.Screencenter.0000.0000.0000..{\fad(695.226)\pos(112.164)\3c&H6ADAF5&}Grade 2
Dialogue: 0.0:01:08.29.0:01:13.96.sign_1408_23_A_Wooden_Bat_is_.Screencenter.0000.0000.0000..{\fad(695.226)\pos(114.186)}Close call with a shotgun
Dialogue: 0.0:01:08.29.0:01:13.96.sign_1408_22_Grade_4.Screenbottom.0000.0000.0000..{\fad(695.226)\pos(112.273)\3c&H585BDA&\q2}Grade 1\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h
Dialogue: 0.0:01:08.29.0:01:13.96.sign_1408_23_A_Wooden_Bat_is_.Screenbottom.0000.0000.0000..{\fad(695.226)\pos(114.295)\q2}Even a tank may be insufficient
Dialogue: 0.0:01:08.74.0:01:09.51.Main.Ijichi.0000.0000.0000..Grade 2.
Dialogue: 0.0:01:09.51.0:01:11.04.Main.Ijichi.0000.0000.0000..It'll be a close call with a shotgun.
Dialogue: 0.0:01:11.04.0:01:11.84.Main.Ijichi.0000.0000.0000..Grade 1.
Dialogue: 0.0:01:11.84.0:01:13.73.Main.Ijichi.0000.0000.0000..Even a tank may be insufficient.
Dialogue: 0.0:01:13.73.0:01:14.98.Main.Ijichi.0000.0000.0000..Then there's special-grade.
Dialogue: 0.0:01:13.96.0:01:19.10.sign_1408_23_A_Wooden_Bat_is_.Screencenter.0000.0000.0000..{\fad(531.1)\pos(114.9)\3c&HF3F4F2&}Close call with a shotgun
Dialogue: 0.0:01:13.96.0:01:19.10.sign_1408_22_Grade_4.Screenbottom.0000.0000.0000..{\fad(531.1)\3c&H6964E1&\q2\pos(112.95)}Grade 1\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h
Dialogue: 0.0:01:13.96.0:01:19.10.sign_1408_23_A_Wooden_Bat_is_.Screenbottom.0000.0000.0000..{\fad(531.1)\pos(114.115)\q2}Even a tank may be insufficient
Dialogue: 0.0:01:13.96.0:01:19.10.sign_1408_22_Grade_4.Screenbottom.0000.0000.0000..{\fad(531.1)\3c&H3100C5&\q2\pos(112.206)}Special-Grade
Dialogue: 0.0:01:13.96.0:01:19.10.sign_1408_23_A_Wooden_Bat_is_.Screenbottom.0000.0000.0000..{\fad(531.1)\q2\pos(114.226)\fscx90}Even footing with a carpet bombing of cluster bombs\h\h\h\h\h
Dialogue: 0.0:01:14.98.0:01:19.10.Main.Ijichi.0000.0000.0000..Let's say you {\i1}might{\i0} be on even footing if \Nyou carpet bomb it with cluster bombs.
Dialogue: 0.0:01:19.27.0:01:20.63.Main.Yuuji.0000.0000.0000..That's real bad!
Dialogue: 0.0:01:20.63.0:01:24.88.Main.Fushiguro.0000.0000.0000..Normally a jujutsu sorcerer on par with \Nthe cursed spirit would take on the mission.
Dialogue: 0.0:01:25.44.0:01:28.02.Main.Fushiguro.0000.0000.0000..On a day like today. \Nthat would be Gojou-sensei.
Dialogue: 0.0:01:28.02.0:01:29.23.Main.Yuuji.0000.0000.0000..I-I see.
Dialogue: 0.0:01:29.77.0:01:31.93.Main.Yuuji.0000.0000.0000..So where is Gojou-sensei?
Dialogue: 0.0:01:32.24.0:01:33.61.Main.Fushiguro.0000.0000.0000..Away on business.
Dialogue: 0.0:01:33.61.0:01:34.46.Main.Yuuji.0000.0000.0000..Huh?
Dialogue: 0.0:01:34.46.0:01:38.80.Main.Fushiguro.0000.0000.0000..He's not someone who should be loafing \Naround at the school in the first place.
Dialogue: 0.0:01:39.19.0:01:41.03.Flashback.Gojou.0000.0000.0000..Don't expect any souvenirs.
Dialogue: 0.0:01:41.28.0:01:45.11.Main.Ijichi.0000.0000.0000..Unfortunately. we're constantly \Nshort-handed in this business.
Dialogue: 0.0:01:45.81.0:01:48.99.Main.Ijichi.0000.0000.0000..You'll often have to undertake \Nmissions beyond your power.
Dialogue: 0.0:01:50.24.0:01:54.48.Main.Ijichi.0000.0000.0000..The current case. however.\Nis an abnormal one. and most urgent.
Dialogue: 0.0:01:54.48.0:01:56.55.Main.Ijichi.0000.0000.0000..Do not fight under any circumstances.
Dialogue: 0.0:01:56.55.0:01:59.02.Main.Ijichi.0000.0000.0000..If you encounter a special-grade.
Dialogue: 0.0:01:59.02.0:02:01.10.Main.Ijichi.0000.0000.0000..your options are to either run or die.
Dialogue: 0.0:02:03.01.0:02:06.10.Main.Ijichi.0000.0000.0000..Please just listen to your fears.
Dialogue: 0.0:02:06.49.0:02:08.64.Main.Ijichi.0000.0000.0000..Do not forget that your mission here
Dialogue: 0.0:02:08.64.0:02:11.90.Main.Ijichi.0000.0000.0000..is strictly the verification \Nand rescue of survivors.
Dialogue: 0.0:02:11.90.0:02:12.69.Main.Mother.0000.0000.0000..Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0.0:02:12.69.0:02:14.22.Main.Mother.0000.0000.0000..Excuse me. where's Tadashi?!
Dialogue: 0.0:02:14.22.0:02:15.54.Main.Staff.0000.0000.0000..Stop! Stay back!
Dialogue: 0.0:02:15.54.0:02:16.84.Main.Staff.0000.0000.0000..Please stay back!
Dialogue: 0.0:02:16.84.0:02:20.59.Main.Mother.0000.0000.0000..Is Tadashi... Is my son Tadashi all right?!
Dialogue: 0.0:02:20.92.0:02:22.35.Main.Staff.0000.0000.0000..{\an8}Please calm down!
Dialogue: 0.0:02:21.47.0:02:22.82.Main.Mother.0000.0000.0000..{\an8}Hey. stop it!
Dialogue: 0.0:02:22.83.0:02:23.64.Main.Staff.0000.0000.0000..{\an8}Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0.0:02:22.83.0:02:25.01.Main.Staff.0000.0000.0000..{\an8}Please stay back! It's dangerous!
Dialogue: 0.0:02:23.64.0:02:24.81.Main.Staff.0000.0000.0000..{\an8}Let me through!
Dialogue: 0.0:02:24.81.0:02:26.71.Main.Ijichi.0000.0000.0000..She's a guardian who was here for a visit.
Dialogue: 0.0:02:27.22.0:02:28.86.Main.Ijichi.0000.0000.0000..Please step away.
Dialogue: 0.0:02:28.86.0:02:32.91.Main.Ijichi.0000.0000.0000..There's a possibility that someone has \Nspread poisonous gas throughout the center.
Dialogue: 0.0:02:33.50.0:02:36.67.Main.Ijichi.0000.0000.0000..We cannot share any more details at this time.
Dialogue: 0.0:02:36.67.0:02:37.74.Main.Mother.0000.0000.0000..No...
Dialogue: 0.0:02:39.65.0:02:41.40.Main.Mother.0000.0000.0000..Why?
Dialogue: 0.0:02:42.14.0:02:45.05.Main.Mother.0000.0000.0000..Why is this happening?!
Dialogue: 0.0:02:47.30.0:02:49.27.Main.Yuuji.0000.0000.0000..Fushiguro. Kugisaki.
Dialogue: 0.0:02:50.04.0:02:51.12.Main.Yuuji.0000.0000.0000..We're gonna save them!
Dialogue: 0.0:02:51.64.0:02:52.71.Main.Kugisaki.0000.0000.0000..Of course we are.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:04.99.0:03:11.95.Show_Title..0000.0000.0000..{\blur1\fad(1191.431)\t(1192.1316.1 \c&H0700D7&\3c&H6659E4&)\t(1317.1941.1 \c&H172918&\3c&H8CCECB&)\t(6197.6529.1 \c&H0F0063&\3c&H222781&)}Jujutsu Kaisen
Dialogue: 0.0:04:24.99.0:04:26.66.Main.Sign.0000.0000.0000..{\pos(320.90)\fnTimes New Roman\b1\c&H171109&\3c&H413829&\shad0\fs30\frx12}Block 2
Dialogue: 0.0:04:25.99.0:04:32.04.Ep_Title_Shadow.Screen.0000.0000.0000..{\fad(526.561)\fs20\pos(612.310)}Episode 4: {\fscx75\fs24}Curse Womb Must Die
Dialogue: 0.0:04:25.99.0:04:32.04.Ep_Title.Screen.0000.0000.0000..{\fad(526.561)\fs20\pos(612.310)}Episode 4: {\fscx75\fs24}Curse Womb Must Die
Dialogue: 0.0:04:29.59.0:04:30.69.Main.Ijichi.0000.0000.0000..{\an8}Be careful.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:32.82.0:04:34.36.Main.Ijichi.0000.0000.0000..I'll put up my Veil.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:34.95.0:04:37.26.Main.Ijichi.0000.0000.0000..Emerge from darkness. blacker than darkness.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:37.47.0:04:39.47.Main.Ijichi.0000.0000.0000..Purify that which is impure.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:47.20.0:04:49.04.Main.Yuuji.0000.0000.0000..It's becoming night!
Dialogue: 0.0:04:49.04.0:04:50.12.Main.Fushiguro.0000.0000.0000..It's Veil.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:50.12.0:04:52.41.Main.Fushiguro.0000.0000.0000..There's a residential area nearby.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:52.41.0:04:54.78.Main.Fushiguro.0000.0000.0000..so this barrier conceals us \Nfrom the outside world.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:54.78.0:04:56.07.Main.Yuuji.0000.0000.0000..That's incredible!
Dialogue: 0.0:04:56.07.0:04:57.29.Main.Kugisaki.0000.0000.0000..Ignorant.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:58.45.0:04:59.19.Main.Fushiguro.0000.0000.0000..Demon Dogs!
Dialogue: 0.0:05:04.80.0:05:07.37.Main.Fushiguro.0000.0000.0000..He'll let us know if the curse gets close.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:07.37.0:05:09.27.Main.Yuuji.0000.0000.0000..Oh. I see!
Dialogue: 0.0:05:09.27.0:05:12.62.Main.Yuuji.0000.0000.0000..Good boy. good boy! We're counting on you. okay?
Dialogue: 0.0:05:16.00.0:05:16.78.Main.Fushiguro.0000.0000.0000..Let's go.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:20.58.0:05:21.47.Main.Fushiguro.0000.0000.0000..Wait!
Dialogue: 0.0:05:24.71.0:05:26.18.Main.Kugisaki.0000.0000.0000..What is this?
Dialogue: 0.0:05:26.81.0:05:29.24.Main.Yuuji.0000.0000.0000..Wh-What's going on in here?
Dialogue: 0.0:05:29.51.0:05:32.66.Main.Yuuji.0000.0000.0000..This is a two-story dorm. isn't it?
Dialogue: 0.0:05:32.91.0:05:36.02.Main.Kugisaki.0000.0000.0000..C-C-Calm down! It's a maisonette.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:36.02.0:05:37.28.Italics.Fushiguro.0000.0000.0000..No. it's not.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:37.92.0:05:40.67.Italics.Fushiguro.0000.0000.0000..It's the deployment of an \NInnate Domain due to cursed energy.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:41.13.0:05:43.42.Italics.Fushiguro.0000.0000.0000..It's my first time seeing one this big.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:44.48.0:05:45.29.Main.Fushiguro.0000.0000.0000..Where's the door?!
Dialogue: 0.0:05:45.50.0:05:46.20.Main.Yuuji.0000.0000.0000..Huh?
Dialogue: 0.0:05:46.47.0:05:49.24.Main.Yuuji.0000.0000.0000..Th-The door's gone!
Dialogue: 0.0:05:49.24.0:05:52.40.Main.Kugisaki.0000.0000.0000..How?! We just came in \Nthrough here. didn't we?!
Dialogue: 0.0:05:52.55.0:05:55.29.Main.Both.0000.0000.0000..What do we do? \NAh. what do we do about this?
Dialogue: 0.0:05:54.56.0:05:55.29.Main.Fushiguro.0000.0000.0000..{\an8}It'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:55.78.0:05:58.50.Main.Fushiguro.0000.0000.0000..The dog remembers the scent of the entrance.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:58.50.0:06:00.43.Main.Both.0000.0000.0000..Oh. my!
Dialogue: 0.0:06:00.43.0:06:02.66.Main.Kugisaki.0000.0000.0000..Good boy! Have some jerky!
Dialogue: 0.0:06:02.66.0:06:04.88.Main.Kugisaki.0000.0000.0000..Have all the jerky you want!
Dialogue: 0.0:06:04.88.0:06:06.34.Main.Fushiguro.0000.0000.0000..You are {\i1}way{\i0} too calm!
Dialogue: 0.0:06:06.34.0:06:08.67.Main.Yuuji.0000.0000.0000..You really are dependable. Fushiguro.
Dialogue: 0.0:06:09.04.0:06:12.52.Main.Yuuji.0000.0000.0000..Thanks to you. we'll be able to \Nrescue people and save ourselves. too.
Dialogue: 0.0:06:15.77.0:06:16.94.Main.Fushiguro.0000.0000.0000..Let's keep moving.
Dialogue: 0.0:06:48.67.0:06:49.69.Main.Kugisaki.0000.0000.0000..Atrocious.
Dialogue: 0.0:06:50.08.0:06:52.82.Main.Fushiguro.0000.0000.0000..That's... three people. right?
Dialogue: 0.0:06:53.30.0:06:55.64.Main.Tag.0000.0000.0000..{\fs14\c&H22190D&\3c&HBDB7A2&\shad0\move(278.274.380.258.1490.2156)}Okazaki Tadashi
Dialogue: 0.0:06:57.74.0:07:01.35.Flashback_Italics.Mother.0000.0000.0000..Is Tadashi... Is my son Tadashi all right?!
Dialogue: 0.0:07:02.70.0:07:04.81.Main.Yuuji.0000.0000.0000..Let's take this body back.
Dialogue: 0.0:07:05.25.0:07:06.20.Main.Kugisaki.0000.0000.0000..Huh?
Dialogue: 0.0:07:06.20.0:07:07.88.Main.Yuuji.0000.0000.0000..It's that woman's son.
Dialogue: 0.0:07:07.88.0:07:08.88.Main.Kugisaki.0000.0000.0000..But...
Dialogue: 0.0:07:08.88.0:07:10.62.Main.Yuuji.0000.0000.0000..His face isn't too badly mangled.
Dialogue: 0.0:07:10.92.0:07:15.27.Main.Yuuji.0000.0000.0000..His mother won't accept it if we tell \Nher he's dead. but we don't have a body.
Dialogue: 0.0:07:17.92.0:07:20.48.Main.Fushiguro.0000.0000.0000..We have to find and verify two more.
Dialogue: 0.0:07:20.48.0:07:22.08.Main.Fushiguro.0000.0000.0000..Leave that body behind.
Dialogue: 0.0:07:22.08.0:07:23.56.Main.Yuuji.0000.0000.0000..Quit joking around!
Dialogue: 0.0:07:23.56.0:07:25.94.Main.Yuuji.0000.0000.0000..We turned around. and the way \Nwe got in here was gone!
Dialogue: 0.0:07:25.94.0:07:27.82.Main.Yuuji.0000.0000.0000..We won't be able to come back for it later!
Dialogue: 0.0:07:27.82.0:07:30.85.Main.Fushiguro.0000.0000.0000..I didn't say to come back for it! \NI said to leave it behind!
Dialogue: 0.0:07:31.89.0:07:34.19.Main.Fushiguro.0000.0000.0000..I have no intention of risking my own life
Dialogue: 0.0:07:34.19.0:07:37.46.Main.Fushiguro.0000.0000.0000..to save someone I had no intention \Nof saving in the first place!
Dialogue: 0.0:07:38.23.0:07:41.50.Main.Yuuji.0000.0000.0000..No intention of saving him? \NWhat do you mean?!
Dialogue: 0.0:07:42.14.0:07:43.86.Main.Fushiguro.0000.0000.0000..This is a juvenile detention center.
Dialogue: 0.0:07:43.86.0:07:47.60.Main.Fushiguro.0000.0000.0000..Jujutsu sorcerers are granted access to \Nall information about the scene beforehand.
Dialogue: 0.0:07:48.90.0:07:50.61.Main.Fushiguro.0000.0000.0000..This Okazaki Tadashi
Dialogue: 0.0:07:50.61.0:07:54.30.Main.Fushiguro.0000.0000.0000..hit a little girl on her way home from \Nschool while driving without a license.
Dialogue: 0.0:07:52.15.0:07:55.12.Main.Screen.0000.0000.0000..{\an7\pos(40.20)\fs14\c&H2A2A2A&\3c&HFAFAFA&\shad0}Youth's Name | Date of Birth\NOkazaki Tadashi | August 9th. 2001\NHighest Education | Sakakidate High School \NDate of Detention | July 20. 2017\NFamily History | Only has his birth mother. Okazaki Chisaki (42)...\N...gone missing. and cannot be contacted...\N...living with his mother in an apartment in Eishuu City...
Dialogue: 0.0:07:55.33.0:07:57.62.Main.Fushiguro.0000.0000.0000..It was his second offense \Nof driving without a license.
Dialogue: 0.0:07:59.32.0:08:04.41.Main.Fushiguro.0000.0000.0000..I know you're stuck on saving lots of people \Nand guiding them to proper deaths.
Dialogue: 0.0:08:05.04.0:08:09.82.Main.Fushiguro.0000.0000.0000..But what are you going to do when someone \Nyou saved kills someone else in the future?
Dialogue: 0.0:08:11.28.0:08:13.60.Main.Yuuji.0000.0000.0000..Then why did you bother saving me?!
Dialogue: 0.0:08:15.94.0:08:17.48.Main.Kugisaki.0000.0000.0000..Cut it out!
Dialogue: 0.0:08:17.48.0:08:20.80.Main.Kugisaki.0000.0000.0000..Christ. what are you two doing?!
Dialogue: 0.0:08:20.80.0:08:22.25.Main.Kugisaki.0000.0000.0000..You're both idiots!
Dialogue: 0.0:08:22.25.0:08:24.95.Main.Kugisaki.0000.0000.0000..Think about the time and place if you—
Dialogue: 0.0:08:26.99.0:08:28.70.Main.Yuuji.0000.0000.0000..Kugisaki?
Dialogue: 0.0:08:28.82.0:08:31.58.Italics.Fushiguro.0000.0000.0000..No way! Demon Dogs should \Nhave sensed the curse!
Dialogue: 0.0:08:35.52.0:08:36.37.Main.Fushiguro.0000.0000.0000..Itadori!
Dialogue: 0.0:08:37.36.0:08:38.46.Main.Fushiguro.0000.0000.0000..We're running!
Dialogue: 0.0:08:38.46.0:08:41.10.Main.Fushiguro.0000.0000.0000..We'll search for Kugisaki la—
Dialogue: 0.0:08:46.64.0:08:47.90.Italics.Fushiguro.0000.0000.0000..There's no mistake.
Dialogue: 0.0:08:48.26.0:08:49.69.Italics.Fushiguro.0000.0000.0000..It's a special-grade.
Dialogue: 0.0:08:49.69.0:08:50.81.Italics.Fushiguro.0000.0000.0000..I can't move.
Dialogue: 0.0:08:51.44.0:08:52.39.Italics.Yuuji.0000.0000.0000..Move.
Dialogue: 0.0:08:52.80.0:08:55.59.Italics.Yuuji.0000.0000.0000..Move! Move! Move! Move!
Dialogue: 0.0:08:56.64.0:08:58.40.Flashback.Grandfather.0000.0000.0000..Help others.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:09.68.0:09:11.16.Main.Fushiguro.0000.0000.0000..Itadori?
Dialogue: 0.0:09:13.63.0:09:14.20.Main.Itadori.0000.0000.0000..Huh?
Dialogue: 0.0:09:18.80.0:09:21.90.Main.Kugisaki.0000.0000.0000..Damn it. where am I?
Dialogue: 0.0:09:21.90.0:09:23.91.Main.Kugisaki.0000.0000.0000..It's so dark. I can't see a thing.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:26.59.0:09:27.71.Italics.Kugisaki.0000.0000.0000..The curse's presence!
Dialogue: 0.0:09:29.27.0:09:31.27.Italics.Kugisaki.0000.0000.0000..How can there be so many?!
Dialogue: 0.0:09:36.42.0:09:37.12.Main.Fushiguro.0000.0000.0000..Nue!
Dialogue: 0.0:09:47.73.0:09:50.47.Italics.Fushiguro.0000.0000.0000..Don't die on me. Itadori and Kugisaki!
Dialogue: 0.0:09:52.17.0:09:54.96.Main.Yuuji.0000.0000.0000..I can't escape after it's gotten this close!
Dialogue: 0.0:09:56.36.0:09:57.60.Main.Yuuji.0000.0000.0000..Hey. Sukuna!
Dialogue: 0.0:09:57.60.0:09:59.56.Main.Yuuji.0000.0000.0000..If I die. you die too. right?
Dialogue: 0.0:09:59.99.0:10:02.00.Main.Yuuji.0000.0000.0000..If you don't want that. then help me out!
Dialogue: 0.0:10:02.40.0:10:03.45.Main.Sukuna.0000.0000.0000..Nope!
Dialogue: 0.0:10:03.72.0:10:05.96.Main.Sukuna.0000.0000.0000..Even if the parts of me inside you die.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:05.96.0:10:09.48.Main.Sukuna.0000.0000.0000..there are eighteen other fragments of my soul.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:09.99.0:10:15.35.Main.Sukuna.0000.0000.0000..Still. irritatingly enough. \NI don't have control of this body.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:15.35.0:10:17.65.Main.Sukuna.0000.0000.0000..If you want to switch. go ahead and switch.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:17.65.0:10:19.47.Main.Sukuna.0000.0000.0000..But once you do.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:20.18.0:10:23.41.Main.Sukuna.0000.0000.0000..I'll kill that brat before the cursed spirit can!
Dialogue: 0.0:10:24.26.0:10:25.63.Main.Sukuna.0000.0000.0000..Then I'll go for that woman!
Dialogue: 0.0:10:25.63.0:10:28.80.Main.Sukuna.0000.0000.0000..She's a lively one. I'll have fun with her.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:29.52.0:10:31.48.Main.Yuuji.0000.0000.0000..I'm not going to let you do that.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:31.60.0:10:32.80.Main.Sukuna.0000.0000.0000..I bet.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:33.29.0:10:37.61.Main.Sukuna.0000.0000.0000..But if you're too focused on me. \Nyour friends are gonna die.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:44.80.0:10:46.32.Italics.Fushiguro.0000.0000.0000..It's not jujutsu.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:47.58.0:10:50.01.Italics.Fushiguro.0000.0000.0000..He just unleashed pure cursed energy.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:53.70.0:10:54.62.Main.Yuuji.0000.0000.0000..Fushiguro!
Dialogue: 0.0:10:55.11.0:10:56.15.Main.Yuuji.0000.0000.0000..Fushiguro!
Dialogue: 0.0:10:56.72.0:10:58.13.Main.Yuuji.0000.0000.0000..Fushiguro!
Dialogue: 0.0:10:59.19.0:11:01.48.Main.Yuuji.0000.0000.0000..Take Kugisaki and get out of here!
Dialogue: 0.0:11:01.79.0:11:05.06.Main.Yuuji.0000.0000.0000..I'll keep this one busy \Nuntil you two are out.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:05.65.0:11:08.32.Main.Yuuji.0000.0000.0000..As soon as you're out. \Ngive me some kind of signal.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:08.59.0:11:12.69.Main.Yuuji.0000.0000.0000..Once you do... I'll switch with Sukuna.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:12.89.0:11:14.55.Main.Fushiguro.0000.0000.0000..You know you can't do that!
Dialogue: 0.0:11:14.55.0:11:16.61.Main.Fushiguro.0000.0000.0000..Not with only one arm against a special-grade!
Dialogue: 0.0:11:16.61.0:11:17.92.Main.Yuuji.0000.0000.0000..Look closer.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:18.81.0:11:20.29.Main.Yuuji.0000.0000.0000..It's having fun.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:20.29.0:11:22.95.Main.Yuuji.0000.0000.0000..It's obviously toying with us.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:23.30.0:11:25.43.Main.Yuuji.0000.0000.0000..I can at least buy us some time.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:25.74.0:11:26.88.Main.Fushiguro.0000.0000.0000..No!
Dialogue: 0.0:11:26.88.0:11:28.08.Main.Yuuji.0000.0000.0000..Fushiguro!
Dialogue: 0.0:11:30.06.0:11:31.01.Main.Yuuji.0000.0000.0000..Please.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:34.19.0:11:35.18.Main.Fushiguro.0000.0000.0000..Demon Dogs!
Dialogue: 0.0:11:38.66.0:11:40.30.Main.Fushiguro.0000.0000.0000..Find Kugisaki!
Dialogue: 0.0:11:43.97.0:11:46.23.Main.Kugisaki.0000.0000.0000..This is my last one.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:48.26.0:11:51.46.Main.Kugisaki.0000.0000.0000..I should've brought a lot more with me.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:00.67.0:12:03.91.Main.Yuuji.0000.0000.0000..Trying to say it's easier to move \Naround in your underwear?
Dialogue: 0.0:12:04.25.0:12:05.79.Italics.Yuuji.0000.0000.0000..What do I do. though?
Dialogue: 0.0:12:05.79.0:12:08.55.Italics.Yuuji.0000.0000.0000..I have no clue how to use cursed energy.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:08.96.0:12:10.51.Italics.Yuuji.0000.0000.0000..But for now. that's fine.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:10.51.0:12:11.80.Italics.Yuuji.0000.0000.0000..I just have to buy ti—
Dialogue: 0.0:12:18.08.0:12:21.08.Italics.Yuuji.0000.0000.0000..What was that? A cursed energy barrier?
Dialogue: 0.0:13:01.04.0:13:02.93.Italics.Yuuji.0000.0000.0000..Ow. ow. ow...
Dialogue: 0.0:13:02.94.0:13:06.42.Italics.Yuuji.0000.0000.0000..It hurts. it hurts. it hurts! Why am I...
Dialogue: 0.0:13:07.08.0:13:10.83.Italics.Yuuji.0000.0000.0000..If only I hadn't picked up \Nthat finger back then...
Dialogue: 0.0:13:12.03.0:13:13.20.Italics.Yuuji.0000.0000.0000..If I hadn't eaten it...
Dialogue: 0.0:13:13.94.0:13:14.80.Italics.Yuuji.0000.0000.0000..If only...
Dialogue: 0.0:13:15.39.0:13:16.36.Italics.Yuuji.0000.0000.0000..If only...
Dialogue: 0.0:13:16.97.0:13:18.13.Italics.Yuuji.0000.0000.0000..Stop!
Dialogue: 0.0:13:18.13.0:13:19.38.Italics.Yuuji.0000.0000.0000..Don't think!
Dialogue: 0.0:13:20.89.0:13:22.22.Italics.Yuuji.0000.0000.0000..No! No!
Dialogue: 0.0:13:22.22.0:13:24.47.Italics.Yuuji.0000.0000.0000..I want to run! I want to run! I want to run!
Dialogue: 0.0:13:25.20.0:13:26.74.Italics.Yuuji.0000.0000.0000..I don't want to die!
Dialogue: 0.0:13:28.52.0:13:29.87.Italics.Yuuji.0000.0000.0000..If I died here...
Dialogue: 0.0:13:29.87.0:13:31.37.Italics.Yuuji.0000.0000.0000..If I actually died...
Dialogue: 0.0:13:31.60.0:13:33.44.Italics.Yuuji.0000.0000.0000..Would that be a proper death?!
Dialogue: 0.0:13:37.62.0:13:41.79.Main.Yuuji.0000.0000.0000..Don't think!
Dialogue: 0.0:13:43.56.0:13:45.28.Flashback_Italics.Grandfather.0000.0000.0000..Help others.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:47.18.0:13:48.21.Italics.Yuuji.0000.0000.0000..Have I...
Dialogue: 0.0:13:48.91.0:13:50.79.Italics.Yuuji.0000.0000.0000..gotten so weak?
Dialogue: 0.0:13:54.06.0:13:56.96.Main.Kugisaki.0000.0000.0000..I know your face now.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:57.21.0:13:59.15.Main.Kugisaki.0000.0000.0000..I swear I'll curse you!
Dialogue: 0.0:14:13.38.0:14:15.18.Main.Fushiguro.0000.0000.0000..We're escaping. Kugisaki!
Dialogue: 0.0:14:15.18.0:14:17.88.Main.Kugisaki.0000.0000.0000..I hate frogs. you know.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:17.88.0:14:19.17.Main.Fushiguro.0000.0000.0000..Yeah. well. sorry!
Dialogue: 0.0:14:26.93.0:14:28.22.Main.Yuuji.0000.0000.0000..I was so full of myself.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:29.62.0:14:31.44.Main.Yuuji.0000.0000.0000..I thought I was strong.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:32.44.0:14:36.18.Main.Yuuji.0000.0000.0000..I thought I was at least strong \Nenough to choose when I died.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:36.76.0:14:38.33.Main.Yuuji.0000.0000.0000..But I was wrong.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:39.81.0:14:42.48.Main.Yuuji.0000.0000.0000..I'm weak!
Dialogue: 0.0:14:43.66.0:14:46.49.Main.Yuuji.0000.0000.0000..I'm far too weak!
Dialogue: 0.0:14:47.31.0:14:50.50.Main.Yuuji.0000.0000.0000..Augh. I don't want to die!
Dialogue: 0.0:14:50.96.0:14:53.28.Main.Yuuji.0000.0000.0000..No! No way!
Dialogue: 0.0:14:53.28.0:14:57.22.Main.Yuuji.0000.0000.0000..But... I {\i1}am{\i0} going to die!
Dialogue: 0.0:14:57.96.0:14:59.62.Italics.Yuuji.0000.0000.0000..A proper death?
Dialogue: 0.0:15:00.17.0:15:02.83.Italics.Yuuji.0000.0000.0000..Yeah. right! Don't be naïve!
Dialogue: 0.0:15:03.85.0:15:06.63.Flashback.Yaga.0000.0000.0000..Jujutsu sorcerers never die without regret.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:08.62.0:15:12.86.Italics.Yuuji.0000.0000.0000..Still. I want to be able to say \Nmy death was a proper one.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:14.60.0:15:17.77.Flashback_Italics.Fushiguro.0000.0000.0000..The negative emotions of mankind \Nbecome the source of curses.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:19.11.0:15:25.03.Italics.Yuuji.0000.0000.0000..So all the hate. fear. regret...
Dialogue: 0.0:15:26.32.0:15:28.32.Italics.Yuuji.0000.0000.0000..Let it all out...
Dialogue: 0.0:15:29.00.0:15:31.04.Italics.Yuuji.0000.0000.0000..And put it in your fist!
Dialogue: 0.0:15:44.98.0:15:46.11.Main.Yuuji.0000.0000.0000..Damn it!
Dialogue: 0.0:15:49.97.0:15:51.38.Italics.Yuuji.0000.0000.0000..That howl...
Dialogue: 0.0:15:56.57.0:15:58.58.Italics.Yuuji.0000.0000.0000..It's Fushiguro's signal.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:06.51.0:16:09.69.Main.Sukuna.0000.0000.0000..What a thoroughly annoying brat.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:13.15.0:16:15.95.Eyecatch_Title..0000.0000.0000..{\blur1\fad(864.1)}Jujutsu Kaisen
Dialogue: 0.0:16:18.66.0:16:21.00.Eyecatch_Title..0000.0000.0000..{\blur1\fad(864.1)}Jujutsu Kaisen
Dialogue: 0.0:16:23.44.0:16:26.26.Main.Sukuna.0000.0000.0000..What a thoroughly annoying brat.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:26.88.0:16:29.57.Main.Sukuna.0000.0000.0000..He's obviously screwing with me.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:32.39.0:16:34.95.Main.Sukuna.0000.0000.0000..Hold on a moment. I'm thinking right now.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:34.95.0:16:38.85.Main.Sukuna.0000.0000.0000..What can I do to make that brat regret this?
Dialogue: 0.0:16:41.21.0:16:45.66.Italics.Sukuna.0000.0000.0000..If I went after him. the brat would \Njust switch back right beforehand.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:46.14.0:16:49.25.Italics.Sukuna.0000.0000.0000..So the thing that would cause \Nhim the most trouble...
Dialogue: 0.0:16:49.76.0:16:51.67.Italics.Sukuna.0000.0000.0000..is probably this.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:51.67.0:16:53.65.Italics.Sukuna.0000.0000.0000..I'll put things back the way they were.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:54.36.0:16:56.77.Main.Sukuna.0000.0000.0000..Hey. let's go kill some kids.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:57.76.0:16:58.87.Main.Sukuna.0000.0000.0000..Follow me.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:06.74.0:17:07.58.Italics.Sukuna.0000.0000.0000..Idiot.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:14.69.0:17:18.11.Main.Sukuna.0000.0000.0000..Ah. shit. I healed this one. too.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:20.11.0:17:21.71.Main.Sukuna.0000.0000.0000..You don't like walks?
Dialogue: 0.0:17:22.44.0:17:26.51.Main.Sukuna.0000.0000.0000..Well. cursed spirits are usually \Nsupposed to stay where they're born.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:26.51.0:17:28.83.Main.Sukuna.0000.0000.0000..Fine. fine. In that case...
Dialogue: 0.0:17:29.76.0:17:32.27.Main.Sukuna.0000.0000.0000..you die here!
Dialogue: 0.0:17:34.99.0:17:36.70.Main.Sukuna.0000.0000.0000..Hey. what's the matter?
Dialogue: 0.0:17:37.20.0:17:39.36.Main.Sukuna.0000.0000.0000..You're not finished already. are you?
Dialogue: 0.0:17:42.00.0:17:45.86.Main.Sukuna.0000.0000.0000..That's it. Come on. try harder.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:54.50.0:17:55.93.Main.Sukuna.0000.0000.0000..Even a cursed spirit
Dialogue: 0.0:17:56.87.0:17:58.92.Main.Sukuna.0000.0000.0000..would miss their arm. right?
Dialogue: 0.0:18:16.10.0:18:18.82.Main.Fushiguro.0000.0000.0000..Please expand the evacuation \Narea to ten kilometers.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:18.82.0:18:20.08.Main.Ijichi.0000.0000.0000..What about you?
Dialogue: 0.0:18:20.48.0:18:23.49.Main.Fushiguro.0000.0000.0000..I'm waiting here for Itadori to return.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:23.49.0:18:24.59.Main.Ijichi.0000.0000.0000..I see.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:24.87.0:18:29.95.Main.Ijichi.0000.0000.0000..After I take Kugisaki-san to the hospital. \NI'll return as quickly as possible.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:30.39.0:18:33.84.Main.Fushiguro.0000.0000.0000..No. there wouldn't be much \Npoint in you staying here.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:34.73.0:18:35.98.Main.Fushiguro.0000.0000.0000..If you want to do something.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:35.98.0:18:39.46.Main.Fushiguro.0000.0000.0000..please ask them to send over \Na sorcerer grade 1 or higher.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:40.03.0:18:41.80.Main.Fushiguro.0000.0000.0000..Not that I imagine any are around.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:42.17.0:18:44.82.Main.Ijichi.0000.0000.0000..I'll do what I can. Later.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:52.72.0:18:56.03.Italics.Fushiguro.0000.0000.0000..If the worst case happens...
Dialogue: 0.0:18:57.12.0:18:58.80.Flashback.Fushiguro.0000.0000.0000..I don't want to let him die.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:58.80.0:19:00.13.Flashback.Fushiguro.0000.0000.0000..They are.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:00.13.0:19:01.53.Flashback.Fushiguro.0000.0000.0000..Please do something about this.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:03.09.0:19:06.09.Italics.Fushiguro.0000.0000.0000.....then it's my responsibility to end him.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:08.75.0:19:11.21.Main.Sukuna.0000.0000.0000..Hey. did you know?
Dialogue: 0.0:19:11.47.0:19:16.21.Main.Sukuna.0000.0000.0000..We're both classified as \Nspecial-grade. apparently.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:16.50.0:19:19.22.Main.Sukuna.0000.0000.0000..Both you and me. man.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:32.08.0:19:33.92.Main.Sukuna.0000.0000.0000..Good job. special-grade.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:33.92.0:19:35.41.Main.Sukuna.0000.0000.0000..Keep trying.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:40.05.0:19:41.88.Main.Sukuna.0000.0000.0000..You look happy.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:41.88.0:19:43.39.Main.Sukuna.0000.0000.0000..Want me to praise you?
Dialogue: 0.0:19:44.07.0:19:50.79.Main.Sukuna.0000.0000.0000..But healing with cursed energy isn't that hard \Nfor cursed spirits. unlike for humans.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:52.21.0:19:55.39.Main.Sukuna.0000.0000.0000..Neither you nor this brat
Dialogue: 0.0:19:56.37.0:19:58.72.Main.Sukuna.0000.0000.0000..really understand
Dialogue: 0.0:19:59.11.0:20:01.51.Main.Sukuna.0000.0000.0000..what curses truly are.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:02.11.0:20:04.72.Main.Sukuna.0000.0000.0000..This is a good opportunity. \Nso I'll show you...
Dialogue: 0.0:20:05.30.0:20:07.98.Main.Sukuna.0000.0000.0000..what real jujutsu is.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:10.30.0:20:11.91.Main.Sukuna.0000.0000.0000..Domain Expansion.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:20.52.0:20:22.30.Main.Sukuna.0000.0000.0000..Malevolent Shrine!
Dialogue: 0.0:20:29.07.0:20:31.94.Main.Sukuna.0000.0000.0000..I was planning to cut you in three slices.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:31.94.0:20:34.00.Main.Sukuna.0000.0000.0000..but you're really weak.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:34.85.0:20:37.96.Main.Sukuna.0000.0000.0000..Oh. yeah. and then there's this.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:38.56.0:20:40.44.Main.Sukuna.0000.0000.0000..I'll be taking this.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:50.45.0:20:52.00.Main.Sukuna.0000.0000.0000..It's over.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:55.81.0:20:57.15.Main.Sukuna.0000.0000.0000..This sucks!
Dialogue: 0.0:20:57.15.0:20:59.21.Main.Sukuna.0000.0000.0000..If you're gonna switch. just do it already!
Dialogue: 0.0:21:03.29.0:21:05.10.Main.Sukuna.0000.0000.0000..What's the matter. brat?
Dialogue: 0.0:22:44.96.0:22:47.51.sign_32727_342_Juju_Stroll.Screen&Voice.0000.0000.0000..Juju Stroll
Dialogue: 0.0:22:47.68.0:22:49.84.Main.Ijichi.0000.0000.0000..Yes. yes. understood.
Dialogue: 0.0:22:49.84.0:22:51.74.Main.Ijichi.0000.0000.0000..Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0.0:22:51.74.0:22:52.52.Main.Ijichi.0000.0000.0000..Yes.
Dialogue: 0.0:22:52.79.0:22:54.72.Italics.Both.0000.0000.0000..Stare...
Dialogue: 0.0:22:55.54.0:22:56.47.Main.Ijichi.0000.0000.0000..What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0.0:22:56.47.0:22:59.03.Main.Kugisaki.0000.0000.0000..You bow while on the phone.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:00.35.0:23:07.03.Main.Ijichi.0000.0000.0000..I just get so wrapped up in creating the feeling \Nof "I'm on the phone!" while on a call...
Dialogue: 0.0:23:07.21.0:23:08.24.Main.Kugisaki.0000.0000.0000..I know what you mean.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:08.24.0:23:13.23.Main.Kugisaki.0000.0000.0000..I've hurt my neck several times dealing \Nwith ingrown hairs while depilating.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:13.23.0:23:15.29.Main.Kugisaki.0000.0000.0000..Of course. I've hurt my pores. too.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:15.29.0:23:17.04.Main.Itadori.0000.0000.0000..Is that really the same?
Dialogue: 0.0:23:17.23.0:23:20.57.Main.Itadori.0000.0000.0000..You're often irritated when \Nyou're on the phone. Fushiguro.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:20.57.0:23:23.70.Main.Fushiguro.0000.0000.0000..That's because of Gojou-sensei. \Nnot the phone.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:23.70.0:23:27.32.Main.Kugisaki.0000.0000.0000..You often wander around when \Nyou're on the phone. Itadori.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:27.32.0:23:28.69.Main.Ijichi.0000.0000.0000..Speaking of phones.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:28.69.0:23:32.80.Main.Ijichi.0000.0000.0000..can you all stay on a call while holding \Nthe phone against your shoulder?
